<td width="150"><br></td>
<td align="center"><b>
<i>Melissodes niveus</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">Robertson, 1895</font></b><br>
<small><i>Melissodes nivea </i>Robertson, 1895; <i>Melissodes &#40;Eumelissodes&#41; nivea </i>Robertson, 1895</small><p>
<a href="/mp/20q?search=Life">Life</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Insecta">Insecta</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Hymenoptera">Hymenoptera</a>
